    <div class="l-header">

      <div class="l-header__content">

        <h1 class="o-logo u-spacing"><span>Refresh Meetup</span> <svg><use xlink:href="#logo-refresh" /></svg></h1>

        <h2 class="u-uppercase">What is Refresh?</h2>
        <p>A meetup for designers and front-end developers. We'll organize talks, discussions, videos and bbq's. Beers included. Topics about UX, design, CSS, JS, workflow, tools and more.</p>

        <h2 class="u-uppercase">When is Refresh?</h2>
        <p>Once every two months on a tuesday evening in Groningen.</p>

        <h2 class="u-uppercase">Need to know more?</h2>
        <p>Read the <a href="https://medium.com/studio-wolf/refresh-the-meetup-for-designers-and-front-end-developers-e86cb77bd360">blog by Studio Wolf</a>. Questions about the meetup or interesting in hosting Refresh in your city? <a href="mailto:aljan@scholtens.me">Let us know</a>.</p>

      </div>

    </div>

